title: Waste of money.
review:
No redeeming aspects at all.

It's like a community centre found a video camera and made the 'film' in their lunch hour.

Give this one a miss.

title: dumb
review: Effects are stupid, acting is stupid, story is stupid, guess the only fans are the people who made it.

title: Thoughts from a huge zombie fan
review:
Poor effects, poor camera shots and angles.. also the story... whats up with that? Lots of selfie shots / ranting in one single shot/area (impressive but it really looses it's quality IMO)

Guy: Don't leave me! Woman: I'm a woman, I am not allowed to think.

What??????????

Can't let the idea go to waste and all the effort tbh, since it was an attempt of making something original so 4/10.
